topic.title: Anyone have SEUS PTGI HRR 2.1 available?
topic.body: I've supported SEUS before (since the creation) and recently unpledged for personal reasons. But now I've tried to repledge and patreon itself won't let me and I've contacted to no avail. So, to the point, anyone have and is willing to share the shader? I have 10 and 11 if anyone wants them.
